980
01:02:07,487 --> 01:02:08,642
<font color=#ffff00>Froulein, there is no other conductor.</font>

981
01:02:08,666 --> 01:02:09,666
<font color=#ffff00>I know what I saw.</font>

982
01:02:09,801 --> 01:02:12,433
<font color=#ffff00>I remember because his voice was high
