983
01:02:12,457 --> 01:02:14,070
<font color=#ffff00>Although I suspect missing one button.</font>

984
01:02:14,206 --> 01:02:15,726
<font color=#ffff00>Sir, I need your pass key immediately.</font>

985
01:02:15,934 --> 01:02:19,536
<font color=#ffff00>We need to find a uniform
