986
01:02:19,678 --> 01:02:21,939
<font color=#ffff00>Thousands of photographs,
any less pair of socks...</font>

987
01:02:22,259 --> 01:02:24,019
<font color=#ffff00>Dressing gowns in every colors, but red...</font>

988
01:02:24,245 --> 01:02:25,885
<font color=#ffff00>still no contraband conduct his uniform.</font>

989
01:02:26,110 --> 01:02:28,376
