01:05:02,301 --> 01:05:04,445
<font color=#ffff00>- Fudge?
- Fudge. It is full of the fudge.</font>

1026
01:05:04,703 --> 01:05:06,364
<font color=#ffff00>You stole from him.</font>

1027
01:05:06,617 --> 01:05:08,071
<font color=#ffff00>You thought you would be found out.</font>

1028
01:05:08,275 --> 01:05:10,248
<font color=#ffff00>That is why you killed him!</font>

1029
01:05:10,446 --> 01:05:11,446
<font color=#ffff00>Yeah.</font>

1030
01:05:12,555 --> 01:05:15,803
<font color=#ffff00>Yeah, you are damn right,
I stole from him.</font>

1031
01:05:15,987 --> 01:05:17,181
<font color=#ffff00>Thousands.</font>

1032
01:05:18,191 --> 01:05:20,739
<font color=#ffff00>I knew his money wasn't honest.</font>

1033
01:05:20,979 --> 01:05:23,932
<font color=#ffff00>Who wondered it would matter
