1034
01:05:24,232 --> 01:05:26,898
<font color=#ffff00>But let me ask you a question.</font>

1035
01:05:27,261 --> 01:05:30,704
<font color=#ffff00>Why would I slaughter my cash cow?</font>

1036
01:05:30,975 --> 01:05:31,987
<font color=#ffff00>I didn't do it.</font>

1037
01:05:32,307 --> 01:05:33,613
<font color=#ffff00>- I didn't kill him!
- He didn't.</font>

1038
01:05:34,610 --> 01:05:35,753
<font color=#ffff00>He didn't.</font>

1039
01:05:36,654 --> 01:05:39,423
<font color=#ffff00>I expect his alibi revolves around me
drinking till the early hours</font>

1040
01:05:39,645 --> 01:05:40,645
<font color=#ffff00>Well, it's true.</font>

1041
01:05:40,755 --> 01:05:44,205
<font color=#ffff00>I saw him having whiskey and remarked
in the lesser quality of American liquor.</font>

1042
01:05:44,422 --> 01:05:46,829
<font color=#ffff00>He offered me a tipple to
