1043
01:05:47,635 --> 01:05:50,182
<font color=#ffff00>We got to arguing politics.
He had some...</font>

1044
01:05:50,983 --> 01:05:54,250
<font color=#ffff00>tom-fool opinions on Stalin I had to
correct, but the man knows his spirits.</font>

1045
01:05:58,279 --> 01:06:00,093
<font color=#ffff00>A word, please, monsieur.</font>

1046
01:06:00,284 --> 01:06:02,124
<font color=#ffff00>You can't confirm you
were with him all night?</font>

1047
01:06:02,277 --> 01:06:04,170
<font color=#ffff00>We smoked and spoke
