1111
01:09:14,266 --> 01:09:15,724
<font color=#ffff00>No. No.</font>

1112
01:09:16,009 --> 01:09:17,143
<font color=#ffff00>But you found him.</font>

1113
01:09:17,425 --> 01:09:18,358
<font color=#ffff00>No.</font>

1114
01:09:18,385 --> 01:09:20,177
<font color=#ffff00>- You found him. You bled him dry.
- No.</font>

1115
01:09:20,454 --> 01:09:24,681
<font color=#ffff00>In order to settle your father's debts
and then finally, to settle...</font>

1116
01:09:24,913 --> 01:09:26,119
<font color=#ffff00>No, no, no.</font>

1117
01:09:26,406 --> 01:09:28,144
<font color=#ffff00>No. It was not...</font>

1118
01:09:28,422 --> 01:09:31,105
<font color=#ffff00>It wasn't like that.
It was not...</font>

1119
01:09:34,420 --> 01:09:36,543
<font color=#ffff00>- Some one, kicking the door.
- Doctor!</font>

1120
01:09:36,817 --> 01:09:38,187
<font color=#ffff00>Covered my face!</font>

1121
01:09:39,997 --> 01:09:41,691
<font color=#ffff00>Alright, this needs to come out now.</font>

1122
01:09:47,419 --> 01:09:49,114
<font color=#ffff00>- I want my bag.
- Of course.</font>

1123
01:09:49,294 --> 01:09:50,364
<font color=#ffff00>It's in my compartment.</font>

1124
01:09:51,314 --> 01:09:52,556
<font color=#ffff00>There will be no fingerprints.</font>

1125
01:09:52,580 --> 01:09:54,528
<font color=#ffff00>The killer was disposing
