1126
01:10:04,787 --> 01:10:07,056
<font color=#ffff00>The killer didn't hit her lung or artery.</font>

1127
01:10:07,344 --> 01:10:08,696
<font color=#ffff00>She's lucky to be alive.</font>

1128
01:10:08,880 --> 01:10:10,098
<font color=#ffff00>You all are.</font>

1129
01:10:10,363 --> 01:10:11,363
<font color=#ffff00>Yes, some genius!</font>

1130
01:10:11,472 --> 01:10:13,617
<font color=#ffff00>Why haven't you solved this case?</font>

1131
01:10:14,257 --> 01:10:16,071
<font color=#ffff00>You must give the man some time here.</font>

1132
01:10:16,073 --> 01:10:17,273
<font color=#ffff00>Yeah? Well...</font>

1133
01:10:17,521 --> 01:10:20,341
<font color=#ffff00>I can't give them much more.
