1138
01:10:31,037 --> 01:10:32,277
<font color=#ffff00>Please, leave me alone.</font>

1139
01:10:32,549 --> 01:10:33,936
<font color=#ffff00>Say something.</font>

1140
01:10:34,108 --> 01:10:36,196
<font color=#ffff00>My friends, the tracks will be
