1141
01:10:36,220 --> 01:10:37,540
<font color=#ffff00>Please return to your rooms.</font>

1142
01:10:37,796 --> 01:10:38,796
<font color=#ffff00>I'm sleeping here..</font>

1143
01:10:39,012 --> 01:10:41,092
<font color=#ffff00>Where everyone can see me
